  "description": "Complete API documentation for Student Request Management component with email notification functionality. All requests marked with ✉️ trigger email notifications.\n\n## Email Notification Events\n\n1. **Create Request** → Sends confirmation to student + notification to all admins/tutors\n2. **Assign Tutor** → Sends assignment notification to student\n3. **Update Status** → Sends status change notification to student\n\n## Setup Instructions\n\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set variables: baseUrl, jwt (student token), adminJwt (admin token), requestId\n3. Ensure server is running with email service configured\n4. Run requests and check email inbox for notifications\n\n## Response Format\n\nAll responses include a `success` flag:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"...\",\n  \"data\": {...}\n}\n```"
}
